{"type":"text","timestamp":1784692916613,"sessionID":"ses_07813ae6bffeXSfNUcMKmjadEz","part":{"id":"prt_f87fc8607001YCaMsFyugzhFon","messageID":"msg_f87fc535e00182Qm12eCe1QNjh","sessionID":"ses_07813ae6bffeXSfNUcMKmjadEz","type":"text","text":"## Objective\n- Execute the detached deep-review loop for the compiled coverage buildout lineage through 10 iterations and synthesis.\n- Write only to the `luna-xhigh` lineage directory, then emit `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:luna-xhigh`.\n\n## Important Details\n- Session: `fanout-luna-xhigh-1784691838667-iv78vk`; executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.6-luna-fast`; `stopPolicy=max-iterations`; `maxIterations=10`.\n- Artifact boundary: `.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-coverage-buildout/review/lineages/luna-xhigh`.\n- Graph/database writes are skipped because the user forbids writes outside the lineage directory.\n- `resource-map.md` is absent.\n- Existing worktree changes outside the lineage were present before this work.\n- Local compiled dist freshness warnings remain active.\n\n## Work State\n### Completed\n- Read `.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/SKILL.md`, workflow YAML, protocol references, and `deep-review` agent definition.\n- Completed phase initialization and created lineage config, state, registry, strategy, and dashboard.\n- Iteration 1 completed and verified; found P1 `F001`: concurrent manifest refreshes can overwrite the same generation due to unlocked `fs.writeFileSync` in `.opencode/bin/lib/compiled-route-manifest.cjs:564-588`.\n- Iteration 2 completed and verified; no new correctness findings.\n- Created iteration prompts, narratives, and deltas for iterations 1 and 2.\n- `verify-iteration.cjs` passed for iterations 1 and 2.\n- `reduce-state.cjs` completed after both iterations.\n\n### Active\n- Security iteration 3 investigation has started.\n- Reviewed