{"type":"text","timestamp":1784693001978,"sessionID":"ses_07813ae6bffeXSfNUcMKmjadEz","part":{"id":"prt_f87fe0afc001boIFEdlpgt4QJd","messageID":"msg_f87fdea49001KhkNr8CC2n1CtZ","sessionID":"ses_07813ae6bffeXSfNUcMKmjadEz","type":"text","text":"The verifier passed, but the reducer correctly showed that a prose-level “disproved” detail does not resolve a fallback finding. Its contract requires the canonical `resolvedFindings` list, so I’m adding that explicit resolution event rather than altering reducer behavior.","time":{"start":1784693000956,"end":1784693001976},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_083acec0b04caea0016a604108ecf08191a0c4d4a0fe7b49f9","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784693020082,"sessionID":"ses_07813ae6bffeXSfNUcMKmjadEz","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_Pq6cTksLiKjKwtktzCSAjbv4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Update File: .opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-coverage-buildout/review/lineages/luna-xhigh/deep-review-state.jsonl\n@@\n {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"review\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-review\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=review target_agent=deep-review\",\"run\":3,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"security: path, flag, and serving boundaries\",\"dimensions\":[\"security\"],\"filesReviewed\":[\".opencode/bin/lib/compiled-route-manifest.cjs\",\".opencode/bin/lib/compiled-routing/011-runtime-engine/lib/resolve.cjs\",\".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/compiled-routing-parity.cjs\",\".opencode/bin/tests/compiled-route-manifest.test.cjs\",\".opencode/bin/compiled-route-sync.cjs\"],\"findingsCount\":1,\"findingsSummary\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":0},\"findingsNew\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":0,\"P2\":0},\"findingDetails\":[{\"findingId\":\"F001\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"category\":\"correctness\",\"finding_class\":\"class-of-bug\",\"title\":\"Concurrent refreshes can lose a generation/policy update\",\"file\":\".opencode/bin/lib/compiled-route-manifest.cjs\",\"line\":588,\"line_range\":\"564-588\",\"description\":\"Refresh reads, compiles, and plain-overwrites without serialization or compare-and-swap.\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\".opencode/bin/lib/compiled-route-manifest.cjs:564-588\",\".opencode/bin/tests/compiled-route-manifest.test.cjs:457-472\"],\"scopeProof\":\"Carried-forward finding from iteration 1.\",\"affectedSurfaceHints\":[\"canonical manifest refresh CLI\",\"activation manifest state\"