 resilience\n+- focus area: malformed inputs, missing artifacts, invalid flags, and recovery behavior\n+- reason: integration surfaces are covered; resilience is the remaining edge-case frontier\n+\n+Review verdict: CONDITIONAL\n","additions":23,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0089-sk-doc-default-routing-cutover/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-coverage-buildout/review/lineages/luna-xhigh/deltas/iter-007.jsonl","relativePath":".opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-coverage-buildout/review/lineages/luna-xhigh/deltas/iter-007.jsonl","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0089-sk-doc-default-routing-cutover/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-coverage-buildout/review/lineages/luna-xhigh/deltas/iter-007.jsonl\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0089-sk-doc-default-routing-cutover/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-coverage-buildout/review/lineages/luna-xhigh/deltas/iter-007.jsonl\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0089-sk-doc-default-routing-cutover/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/013-compiled-