 Line 273: **Outputs:** Spec folder with `{artifact_dir}/` packet (flat-first `{spec_folder}/review/`, with `{spec_folder}/review/{packet}-pt-{NN}/` only for separated nested-phase packets), `review-report.md`, optional `resource-map.md`, state files, and `STATUS=<OK|FAIL|CANCELLED>`\n\n  Line 281: | Synth | Synthesize | Build finding registry, emit `review/resource-map.md`, deduplicate, compile `review/review-report.md` | `review/resource-map.md`, `review/review-report.md` (9 sections) |\n\n  Line 282: | Save | Preserve | Refresh continuity update in canonical spec docs | canonical spec doc updated via `generate-context.js` |\n\n  Line 322: - `node .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/dist/memory/generate-context.js /tmp/save-context-data-<session-id>.json [spec-folder]`\n\n  Line 355: Artifacts: review/review-report.md, review/resource-map.md (unless `--no-resource-map`), [N] iteration files in review/, continuity update in canonical spec docs refreshed\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0089-sk-doc-default-routing-cutover/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep-research-confirm.yaml:\n  Line 171:       After all lineages complete, jump directly to phase_synthesis — skip phase_init and\n\n\n(Results truncated. Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":100,"truncated":true},"title":"phase_synthesis|review-report|synthesize|generate-context|emit-resource-map","time":{"start":1784693592070,"end":1784693592081}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0db580ddc324a744016a604357000481919e15f55a1eac971d"}},"id":"prt_f88070c21001wh414hy0ODV5xH","sessionID":"ses_07813ae6bffeXSfNUcMKmjadEz","messageID":"msg_f880700560011Kw5MprsghsGaA"}}
